---
title: Thai-Spiced Chicken Schnitzel with Sesame Fries & Creamy Slaw
description: Spice up tonight’s schnitzel with our flavour-packed spice blend, coating the chicken in a crunchy breadcrumb and cooking until it shines golden brown. It’s not a schnitzel though without a side of fries. We’re baking them in a scattering of sesame seeds to go with the spiced chicken. Things are certainly getting fun.
